;\n            }\n        } finally {\n            executor.shutdownNow();\n            assertTrue(executor.awaitTermination(2, TimeUnit.SECONDS));\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void configMxBeanMutatesRuntimePoolLimitsAndCredentials() throws SQLException {"}]}
